data_table.description: The data table contains sample attributes including sequencing status, when sample was generated, source of sample, and analyte type.

variable.name: DOL
variable.description: Day of life in which the sample was generated

variable.name: SOURCE
variable.description: Source of sample (e.g. stool, palm, oral)

variable.name: ANALYTE_TYPE
variable.description: Type of analyte (e.g. DNA, 16S rRNA, etc)
